### Create an event
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "title": "Sample Event",
  "description": "Testing event creation manually",
  "category": "music",
  "startDateTime": "2026-04-10T18:00:00.000Z",
  "endDateTime": "2026-04-10T20:00:00.000Z",
  "capacity": 100,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.png",
  "location": {
    "type": "in-person",
    "venueName": "Test Hall",
    "address": "123 Main St",
    "latitude": 37.7749,
    "longitude": -122.4194
  }
}
